what a fucked up day. it all started by wakeing up and doing my usual rutine of being slow as hell. i did my usual sprinting up the hill so i could get to the stop befor the bus. so i finaly rode my bus to school. when i got to school i had a detention were i just sat and listen 2 a bunch of seniors talk about peanut and crack sandwitches. after finaly getting out of my detention i had to run to my locker to put my shit away and grab my binder. as i ran to first period i became late and got another detention. as i waited to take a easy joke of a test which i just guessed on, i started to feel sick from all the runnin. so i finally make it through first and 2nd period were we just watched a fucked up movie..The Odyssey and filled out surveys on how we thought the school year was so far, which i put dont know for all the answers.my 3rd perios teacher made us take 2 quizes 2day becuase shes a bich and never misses a day of teaching us biology.4th period i listen to a girl call herself a bitch and say sum other stuff in spanish over and over again for like an hour straight. after lunch i went to my food class to take an insanely hard test (thank god i had half the study guide or else i would of done really bad).  when i got 2 math mrs. fettehof wouldnt shut up and she made us take note like always.  now that the day was over i have another 2 shitty days to look forward to.well mayb one fridays are never bad days for me. unless in called to the office during 4th period, which would piss the hell out of me cuase my class would b at the bowling alley without me.but that wouldnt happen now unless i brought another water gun to school.
